{"tid":2222721,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"理大生藏摺刀原定今日判刑　裁判官劉綺雲取錯報告需押後再判 期間被告要繼續還押","createTime":"2020-09-29T09:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T09:49:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e77b1965c5b3dabcefa7a99e4aa67885ebf088c1","tid":2222721,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:31:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9898&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXEYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=605e2e68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9898</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第五庭 <br />\n#劉綺雲裁判官 <br />\n#判刑 #1209旺角<br />\n<br />\n陳(18) <br />\n<br />\n控罪1：在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器 <br />\n控罪2：管有適合作非法用途的工具<br />\n<br />\n劉官甫開庭便指出即使本案被告教導所報告顯示年紀適合，然而，在法例（第245章33c條）下，此案之判刑，教導所並非適合選項。<br />\n<br />\n由於上次法庭未有下達指示取勞教中心報告及更生中心報告，故須再次押後，其間繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2020年10月13日0930東區裁判法院判刑。<br />\n<br />\n直播員按：由於被告剪了個清爽的髮型，故他不斷掃頭，十分精神，亦有不時望向旁聽席"},{"pid":"c53d72a26c0759c3436fcaf3ea938321efee68dc","tid":2222721,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"案件原定今天(29日)在東區法院判刑，但主審女裁判官劉綺雲判刑前才發覺自己之前「甩轆」，案件要再押後兩個星期才可判刑，期間被告要繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官於本月16日裁定被告罪成後，下令索取教導所和背景報告，以作為判刑時的參考。惟裁判官今天表示剛發現，以被告的年齡，在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪只能判處監禁、勞教中心或更生中心等刑罰，因此把案件押後至10月13日判刑，以等候勞教中心和更生中心報告。"},{"pid":"9beba4b67bf0ba81b620e0b0458a14cec3ecd0a1","tid":2222721,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43573fb9ce4938d9daa1ddc6f952c5937ffa75f1","tid":2222721,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9beba4b67bf0ba81b620e0b0458a14cec3ecd0a1","tid":2222721,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db515b146bd0a41c2ed3e652ac7da10aae7fd27","tid":2222721,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"白白坐多半個月！"},{"pid":"38ea6d65711a6baa1e5e195d2515693363f4d3e4","tid":2222721,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0db515b146bd0a41c2ed3e652ac7da10aae7fd27","tid":2222721,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"白白坐多半個月！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044f5ab49915b1719c80463ea158e7be591e102d","tid":2222721,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0db515b146bd0a41c2ed3e652ac7da10aae7fd27","tid":2222721,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"白白坐多半個月！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:38:08.000Z","msg":"明玩野"},{"pid":"9eabe8349d1a9e6f89c520c290b7348ff4365e85","tid":2222721,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0db515b146bd0a41c2ed3e652ac7da10aae7fd27","tid":2222721,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislik